Package io.github.waileong.fcm.service.domain

Class FcmAndroid.Builder

java.lang.Object
io.github.waileong.fcm.service.domain.FcmAndroid.Builder
Enclosing class:
FcmAndroid
public static final class FcmAndroid.Builder extends Object
A builder class for creating FcmAndroid instances.

This builder follows the builder pattern to facilitate the construction of FcmAndroid instances with various configuration options set. It supports chaining of methods to configure an instance.
